data.description: Welcome to this stunning 10 acre property where the opportunities are endless!  The amazing 42x70 insulated pole barn with concrete floors will make any enthusiast say “Oh Wow!”  Do you have livestock or have been looking for the right place with adequate space?  This property offers abundant space for livestock with a second barn, 3 stalls and a tack room.  To top it all off there are 2 gated pastures surrounded by electric high tensile fencing for your livestock.  The expansive 2,200 plus square feet single story home is wrapped in steel siding and a steel roof for low maintenance.  This 3 bedroom, 3 bath home offers a vaulted kitchen and living room ceiling for an open concept feel; split bedroom floor plan provides for added private living spaces.  The attached heated 3 car garage with floor drains is added bonus for plenty of vehicle parking and ample space.  Call to see today!
